About : 
Sysmon is a Windows system service and device driver that monitors system activity and logs events in the Windows event log.
Sysmon is free, easy to install, and it provides more detailed information than the Windows security logs. 
QRadar uses the forwarded logs to detect advanced threats on Windows endpoints.

To graphically create the configuration of sysmon
https://github.com/nshalabi/SysmonTools/blob/master/README.md


